videos.description: Kamar Baldwin zips a back-door pass to a diving Christian David for the uncontested finish in the first half.
videos.headline: Butler's Baldwin skips back-door pass to David for lay-in

videos.description: Butler's Paul Jorgensen attacks the rim and floats a layup that is rejected by Phil Booth at the apex.
videos.headline: Villanova's Booth climbs ladder for tenacious swat
